wiki.summary: "Oye" is a duet from Argentinan singers TINI and Sebastián Yatra. After the release of “CRISTINA”, a song by Sebastián Yatra released in March 2019, “Oye” was used to continue telling the story, a single that is part of TINI's third studio album. In it we can see its protagonist (TINI being the character "Cristina") in the moments after her departure and break with the other character in question, that is, Sebastián Yatra. Read more on Last.fm.
